Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思啦親 等人家很久了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹嘛啊 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就沒點羞恥心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 資料準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你那方面呢 有好素材了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼假設也能令人期待了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}慘了 有說過做假設這回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}富農千反田的宅邸在神山市可是最高級別的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看起來很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是因為騎車很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乘著風 憑著自己的腳力前賓士的那…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不對 我問的是你高中生活的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 玫瑰色的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管身邊的人怎樣 我的基本屬性都是玫瑰色的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你那不如叫鮮粉紅更合適
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是這樣子的話 奉太郎就是灰色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前也聽你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是這個卻沒有貶低你的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的基本屬性是鮮粉紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰想把我染成玫瑰色都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會被染上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說不定你已經被染上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說看到我我在總務委員和手藝社的忙碌生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你才說這樣的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論怎麼樣 我還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會被染上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要想貶低你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就會說你是無色的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也沒打算讓你喜歡上我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}期中考怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管哪科都是平均分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不愧為灰色的奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}漸漸能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就是千反田家的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}走吧 千反田她們在等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}奉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}侍從會不會出來迎接呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在此恭候多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請隨便坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們沒有遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}與和式客廳這麼格格不入的男生真是少見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}研討會開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天 就45年前發生在古籍研究社事件進行研討
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是能夠接近到真相的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我打算登載在今年的社刊上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}首先分發資料並進行報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後對此進行提問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接著是報告者的假設
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最後是假設的研究討論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 會議主持做的不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼第一個報告的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…從誰開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}…才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰都可以啊 千反田從你開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也好 那麼從我開始大家順時針輪下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我調查的正是「冰菓」這本社刊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其中涉及到的45年前的那件事的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有這篇序文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以從中可以找出的事實
